    <h2>1. Introduction to Context/Frame</h2>
    <p>Flow is all about living, understanding the law of momentum, and what is most upstream will have outsized impact on your world. The principles of Flow can be applied to consciousness, energy, domains of life, as it all relates to an emergent prosses of life seeking to become more efficient.
      "Go with the flow" is a common phrase that means to adapt to the current situation or to let things happen naturally. It suggests a state of being in harmony with the current circumstances and a willingness to let go of control and expectations. This is essence is what happens when you aren't wasting energy, things will flow easier and more effortlessly.
    </p>
